    L2 -- No --> L4{Host key verification failed?}
    L4 -- Yes --> L5[Remove stale known_hosts entry and reconnect]
    L4 -- No --> L6{Port 22 blocked / timeout?}
    L6 -- Yes --> L7[Use HTTPS or SSH over port 443]
    L6 -- No --> L8[Check repo permission and SSH config]
    L -- Yes --> M{Repo accessible?}
    M -- No --> M1[Check repo access rights and remote URL]
    M -- Yes --> J

    K --> N{Destination directory exists?}
    N -- Yes --> N1[Remove folder or clone into another directory]
    N -- No --> O{Permission denied on filesystem?}
    O -- Yes --> O1[Fix folder ownership or clone elsewhere]
    O -- No --> P{Disk full?}
