## 11. Full End-to-End Debug Sequence

Use this in order when `git clone` fails:

```bash
git --version
git config --list --show-origin
env | grep -i proxy
nslookup github.com
ping github.com
curl -I https://github.com
ssh -T git@github.com
df -h
pwd
ls -la
GIT_TRACE=1 GIT_CURL_VERBOSE=1 git clone https://github.com/user/repo.git
```

If using SSH:
```bash
GIT_SSH_COMMAND="ssh -vvv" git clone git@github.com:user/repo.git
```

